_sText:
This is my 3rd map. My friends encourage me to make a maze map. So here it is! A colourful yet maybe a confusing map to play!

This map Features : 
2 Secret doors 
1 Secret room
2 Secret way which leads to above the map
Flooded map 
Lots and lots of traps so BEWARE!
1 Pit of death


If there are any bugs or etc. Please report!!!!



- Version 2 releasing soon!
